FIG. 2 is a view of a kinematic transmission system fitted in the fixed frame;


FIG. 3 is a perspective view of a circuit breaker according to the invention;


FIG. 4 is an outline diagram of an opening device of the circuit breaker poles, in the open position;


FIG. 5 is an outline diagram of a circuit breaker loading device with energy storage, in the loaded position;


FIG. 6 is a perspective view of a part of the circuit breaker loading device;


FIG. 7 is a perspective view showing operation of an operating lever according to the invention in conjunction with the circuit breaker opening and loading devices;


